next_episode_to_air.overview: Silvério Tasso, is the prey of a new TV show, which will bring a group of 5 hunters on an island to hunt their prey, the public is deciding his fate through a vote, and the only thing in his mind, is the prize of 50.000EUR.

overview: A new show is coming to TV : 1 prey, 5 hunters, 1 island, 200 cameras, no way out. The prey is Silvério " The Executioner " a Sargent of the marines.
